  "code": "%% Integrated Proposal - Policy View\ngraph TD\n  %% Governance / Policy\n  G0[IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream]\n  G1[IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController]\n  G2[IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode]\n\n  %% CLEAR Core\n  subgraph CORE[IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode]\n    direction LR\n    KMS[IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic]\n    MQ[IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker]\n    WN[IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController]\n    DB[IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic]\n    MET[IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController]\n    KMS-->MQ-->WN-->DB-->MET\n  end\n\n  %% Edge / Municipal\n  subgraph EDGE[IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream]\n    direction TB\n    W1[IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic]\n    W2[IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic]\n  end\n\n  %% AI / Audit\n  subgraph AI[IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode]\n    A1[IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic]\n    A2[IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode]\n  end\n\n  %% Flows\n  G1-- \"決済依頼（バーチャルデビット/トークン認証）\" -->G2\n  G2-- \"Txイベント（When/Who/Whom/Coin/Value）\" -->EDGE\n  EDGE-- \"Witnessログ送信（非同期）\" -->CORE\n  CORE-- \"整合証跡（Merkle Root / 署名）\" -->G0\n  AI-- \"AI結果の監査証跡付与\" -->CORE\n  G0-- \"方針・KPI（E-MAD）\" -->MET\n",
