      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "理解，G2→EDGE是Tx事件，然后EDGE→CORE是witness日志的异步发送。CORE处理完后要返回整合证迹给G0，包含Merkle Root和签名。",
