      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，CORE→G0是闭环的关键，Merkle Root保证不可篡改。另外G0还要下发方针和KPI到MET，E-MAD指标直接驱动执行控制器调整策略。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "G0",
        "MET"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "G0到MET的边加上了。我检查一下：现在CORE内部有KMS、MQ、WN、DB、MET，但WN和MET都是ActuatorController标签，DB和KMS都是PLC_Logic，这种标签复用没问题吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
